svg.title: A floor plan with six bedrooms, three on each side of a large hallway running between them, stairs leading down to the main floor, and a second set of stairs leading up to the top floor behind doors labelled “swinging door to servants’ stairs.” The two bedrooms in the back right connect to each other via a dressing room, and both also have external doors to a stone balcony, from which stairs lead down to the grounds.
